Author:
	Dominic Canare
	dom@domstyle.net

Requirements:
	Kivy         >= 1.0.6   [ kivy.org ]
	reacTIVision >= 1.4     [ reactivision.sourceforge.net ]

Description:
	An application for generating calibration.grid files for use with reacTIVision.

How to use:
	1. Delete your existing calibration.grid file
	2. Start reacTIVision
	3. Start main.py
	4. Touch and hold each target
	5. Press escape
	   * New calibration.grid file is saved on disk
	6. Restart reacTIVision w/ new calibration.grid

